snippet.title: "Summit" first look trailer for Playdate
snippet.description:
A first look at Summit, my new Playdate game. 

Summit is an exhilarating mountain climbing game that requires precision platforming. Players embark on an epic journey to conquer the mountain by overcome puzzle platforming obstacles and master climbing techniques.
